data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in scenic Imlay City! With spacious bedrooms, plenty of natural light, and a full basement, this one has everything you need. Basement features poured walls, extra tall, with galvanized 2x4s ready to finish. Permits pulled for basement bathroom, multiple drops in basement, customize your setup! Schedule your private showing today!
